Hi again! 
This time i made a new poolparty no rush map.
The only way to rush in this map is to swim through a tunnel in the pool to the other side. It should be only used if someone is afk. 
Everyone who tries to rush will be punished with a instant kill.
I tested it with my clan on our 16 slot server and i am not lieng the gameplay is great.

Yeah thats it.. give it a try ;-)
